{
  "name": "HRBot — WA Inbound AI Agent",
  "nodes": [

    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "wa-inbound",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "WA Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [0, 300]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "text",
        "responseBody": "OK",
        "options": { "responseCode": 200 }
      },
      "id": "respond-immediately",
      "name": "Respond 200",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [220, 160]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const body = $input.first().json.body ?? $input.first().json;\nconst from    = String(body.from ?? '').replace(/^\\+/, '');\nconst message = String(body.message ?? '').trim();\nconst orgId   = String(body.org_id ?? '');\nif (!from || !message || !orgId) throw new Error('Missing fields: ' + JSON.stringify({ from, message, orgId }));\nreturn [{ json: { from, message, org_id: orgId } }];"
      },
      "id": "parse-payload",
      "name": "Parse Payload",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [220, 300]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.SUPABASE_URL }}/rest/v1/users?wa_number=eq.{{ $json.from }}&organization_id=eq.{{ $json.org_id }}&select=id,full_name,role,wa_number,organization_id&limit=1",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "apikey",        "value": "={{ $env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE }}" },
            { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "fetch-user",
      "name": "Fetch User",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [440, 300]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.SUPABASE_URL }}/rest/v1/wa_sessions?wa_number=eq.{{ $('Parse Payload').item.json.from }}&organization_id=eq.{{ $('Parse Payload').item.json.org_id }}&select=messages&limit=1",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "apikey",        "value": "={{ $env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE }}" },
            { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE }}" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "fetch-history",
      "name": "Fetch History",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [440, 460]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const payload  = $('Parse Payload').first().json;\nconst userArr  = $('Fetch User').first().json;\nconst user     = Array.isArray(userArr) ? userArr[0] : userArr;\nconst histArr  = $('Fetch History').first().json;\nconst session  = Array.isArray(histArr) ? histArr[0] : histArr;\nconst history  = session?.messages ?? [];\n\nconst today = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { timeZone:'Asia/Kolkata', weekday:'long', day:'numeric', month:'long', year:'numeric' });\nconst time  = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-IN', { timeZone:'Asia/Kolkata', hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit' });\n\nconst systemPrompt = `You are HRBot, an AI HR assistant for WhatsApp. Today is ${today}, ${time} IST.\n\nUser: ${user?.full_name ?? 'Unknown'} | Role: ${user?.role ?? 'employee'} | OrgID: ${payload.org_id} | UserID: ${user?.id ?? ''}\n\nRules:\n- Always reply in WhatsApp-friendly format (use *bold*, _italic_, bullet points)\n- For task creation/updates, confirm details before calling the tool (ask: \"Shall I proceed? (Yes/No)\")\n- If user confirms with yes/ok/proceed/haan — call the tool immediately\n- If user cancels with no/cancel/nahi — acknowledge and stop\n- Keep replies concise and action-oriented\n- Dates: accept natural language (\"next Monday\", \"17 June\") and convert to YYYY-MM-DD\n- Priority values: low / medium / high\n- Status values: pending / in_progress / done / cancelled\n\nAvailable tools: list_tasks, create_task, update_task, check_in, check_out, check_leave_balance, apply_leave, list_leaves, daily_briefing, my_attendance, team_attendance, help`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    from:          payload.from,\n    message:       payload.message,\n    org_id:        payload.org_id,\n    user_id:       user?.id ?? '',\n    user_name:     user?.full_name ?? 'there',\n    user_role:     user?.role ?? 'employee',\n    history:       JSON.stringify(history.slice(-10)),\n    system_prompt: systemPrompt,\n  }\n}];"
      },
      "id": "build-context",
      "name": "Build Context",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [660, 380]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "llama-3.3-70b-versatile",
        "options": { "maxTokens": 600, "temperature": 0.2 }
      },
      "id": "groq-model",
      "name": "Groq Llama 3.3",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGroq",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [880, 560],
